By: Mechthild of Magdeburg
---
God frees the simple soul and makes it wise in His love. Ah! sweet dove,
thy feet are red, thy wings are smooth, thy mouth is true, thine eyes are
beautiful, thy head composed, thy wanderings happy, thy flight swift.
